item.title: indy 500 - b00ya
item.description: So this weekend was quite somthing. Friday night I went out with friends to a coupl eclubs. and hung out with “rockstars.” it was fun. They are all very nice. And strangly.. a high number of them are apparently computer people. it is wierd. I ended up staying out til 5 that night which was a shock to myself. I didn’t mean to at all. heh… whoopsso after a late start.
